    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay if you say it's okay... also my doctor is actually super hard to get a hold of right now and i'm starting to feel a bit of a fever too. should i try taking some of those ciprofloxacin pills i have in my cabinet just in case it's a bacterial infection? i really don't want to wait days for a call back if i can just treat it now.",
